The file bioperl-1.0.patch is a patch file that will bring a virgin
Bioperl 1.0 distribution up to version 1.01.  This version contains
certain fixes that allow the wildcard search feature of GBrowse to
work.

Here are the patch steps:

 1. unpack bioperl-1.0.tar.gz
    gunzip -c bioperl-1.0.tar.gz | tar xvf -

 2. enter bioperl-1.0
    cd bioperl-1.0

 3. apply the patch
    patch -p1 < ../Generic-Genome-Browser-1.38/extras/bioperl-1.0.patch

Modify the last command for the actual location of the patch file.
